  <summary date="2023-06-20T12:24:20Z" status="Introduced in House">Travel Trailer and Camper Tax Parity Act

This bill modifies the tax deduction for floor plan financing interest to include in the term motor vehicles eligible for such financing any trailer or camper that is designed to provide temporary living quarters for recreational, camping, or seasonal use and is designed to be towed by, or affixed to, a motor vehicle.</summary>
